# btaa-geo-api-schema(1)

## NAME

btaa-geo-api schema - inspect searchable fields and OGC schema documents

## SYNOPSIS

`btaa-geo-api schema COMMAND`

## COMMANDS

- `fields`
- `facets`
- `filters`
- `search-params`
- `queryables`
- `sortables`

## EXAMPLES

```bash
btaa-geo-api schema facets
btaa-geo-api schema queryables --output json
btaa-geo-api schema sortables
```

## API ENDPOINTS

- `GET /api/v1/ogc/collections/btaa-records/queryables`
- `GET /api/v1/ogc/collections/btaa-records/sortables`
